reviews.text: Quite lot of choices on meals. A good rest place for road trip

They have delicious Dutch snacks like frikandellen, kroketten (croquettes), bitterballen en kaassouffles. Fries and a snack is 40HKD and you'll get a drink included. For 12 HKD extra you get a an Illy coffee with it. 

They also have all other kinds of western and Chinese food. Nice place in case you're in the neighborhood.
Great place, there is dog friendly
